Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%B7c-L%E1%BA%ADp/Th%E1%BB%A9-v%E1%BA%ADn-Nham-qu%E1%BA%BF/poem-8AXVPnYfEzJ1eUATVTNT7A">Thứ vận “Nham quế” - 次韵巖桂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%B7c-L%E1%BA%ADp/author-zIoQcPR3i27SwqkfsWlTXQ">Khương Đặc Lập</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-t%C3%B2ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-%C3%81-ph%C3%B3-H%C3%A0-T%C3%A2y-ph%C3%A1n-quan/poem-pJIF07o2Qkh5pVVW0kebdg">Tống tòng đệ Á phó Hà Tây phán quan - 送從弟亞赴河西判官</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%C3%A2u-X%E1%BB%A9-C%C6%A1/V%E1%BB%8Dng-B%E1%BB%93ng-Lai-Du-h%E1%BB%A9ng/poem-Uoy2mSjnk7btxI4Fq9Zp3A">Vọng Bồng Lai - Du hứng - 望蓬萊—遊興</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%C3%A2u-X%E1%BB%A9-C%C6%A1/author-Xdrx9PY_HQVilIv5qP5QxQ">Khâu Xứ Cơ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-T%E1%BA%AFc-T%E1%BB%AB/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-Gia-D%E1%BB%A5-quan-c%E1%BA%A3m-ph%C3%BA/poem-hPo4dFacW73EYxpwmHQtzw">Xuất Gia Dụ quan cảm phú - 出嘉峪關感賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-T%E1%BA%AFc-T%E1%BB%AB/author-JAv5RkZakjKTfe65gwrmsQ">Lâm Tắc Từ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
